  </div>

  <p style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:7pt;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:8px;">Galois Relationship Framing — Apply Exactly</p>
  <div class="framing-grid">
    <div class="framing-good">
      <div class="framing-lbl">✓ Correct</div>
      <div class="framing-item">
        "primary research partner"<br>
        "preferred structural access to Galois's R&D"<br>
        "works alongside Galois"<br>
        "Galois-to-ExistX pipeline"<br>
        "Galois provides research; ExistX operationalizes"
